# Miniprogram cloudfunctions dir: holds a copy of the api-router bundle (14.5MB)
# that wx devtools expects to exist locally for `wx.cloud.callFunction` upload.
# Real deployment is on CloudBase side, so this is a local-build artifact only.
# Phase 7 added the dir; CP-6.5 added the gitignore rule.
apps/miniprogram/cloudfunctions/
cloudbaserc.fn-secrets.json
cloudbaserc.fn-all.json

